hopobject.body: Can you hear me OK? tamsulosin hydrochloride modified release tablets 0.2mg From what little he has told us about himself, it is possible to detect a sense of regret that he didn’t do something else – or, at least, something more – with his life. “I don’t want to be a rock star forever,” he said in the 1970s, “playing Las Vegas to old ladies.” The same worry was on his mind at Glastonbury where he told the BBC: “Everyone wants to have done more things. It’s slightly intellectually undemanding being a rock singer, but you make the best of it.”
